Things to do
Make changes to a reservation
Need to add a traveler, change the date, or make another adjustment? Not a problem! In most cases, you can change your booking up to 24 hours before your activity. However, please check the “Terms and Conditions” section of your ticket for the detailed policy for your specific activity.
To request a change to your booking:
Go to your Bookings page
Find the booking you need to adjust.
From this page you are able to get your tickets, change date, edit the traveler information, change your tour option or cancel your booking.
 You will receive a confirmation email when your change request has been completed.
